      "title": "Cultural Safety Checklist (Complete before publishing)\\n\\n- Language: Te reo used correctly (macrons, meaning) ☐\\n- Tikanga: Portrayals are respectful/accurate ☐\\n- Whakapapa: Connections and attributions retained ☐\\n- Local iwi: Context aligns or is flagged for review ☐\\n- Sensitive content: Marked for Kaitiaki review ☐\\n- Student safety: Inclusive, strengths-based framing ☐\\n",
